snippet.title: Raziel: Dungeon Arena - Hero Sneak Preview
snippet.description:
Here's a sneak peak at the art style of Raziel: Dungeon Arena. You can take a look at some of the heroes you'll be able to unlock early in the game!

Pre-Register Here: http://raze.wonderent.net/index.php?m=pc&c=Raze&a=init&cid=1
Official Website: http://raze.wonderent.net/

Music By: Electric Romeo - Immediate Music from album Themes for Orchestra and Choir 2 - Abbey Road
